'''Peter King''' served as make-up and hair designer for [[The Lord of the Rings (film series)|''The Lord of the Rings'' (film series)]], for which he won the 2003 '''[http://www.oscar.com/ Academy Award]''' for Best Makeup (alongside [[Richard Taylor]]). He reprised this role in [[The Hobbit (film series)|''The Hobbit'' (film series)]], for which he received a nomination at the 2012 Academy Awards.

